{"title":"雪落家乡（外一首）","authors":["李葆刚"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":2,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪落家乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李葆刚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往事一样的雪落满家乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"封住了门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊烟摸着天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那干柴垛能燃烧很多思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终被落雪困住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屋檐下的铁犁如梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那铧尖闪着忧伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似落雪的月色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲望着窗外的雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起该选种了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惬意的脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已是田野复苏"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}